        ## Terminology

        - `text`: Verbatim
        - `<arg>`: Required Argument
        - `[arg]`: Optional Argument
        - `<add|delete>`: Required Multiple Choice
        - `[add|delete]`: Optional Multiple Choice

        ## Navigation

        - `cd <directory>`: **C**hange **D**irectory
            - Moves your current directory (AKA Working Directory) to another
            location.
        - `pwd`: **P**rint **W**orking **D**irectory
            - Outputs your current directory.
